/**
 * @title SchnorrOffchain
 *
 * @notice Provides offchain Schnorr signature functionality
 *
 * @dev
 *
 * @custom:references
 *      - [ERC-XXX]: ...
 *
 * @author verklegarden
 * @custom:repository github.com/verklegarden/crysol
